@startuml
title Citizen Verification and Contact Matching Flow

start

:Receive phone/email from Case intake or Agent action;
:Search Salesforce Contact by MDM ID, phone, and email;

if (Salesforce Contact found?) then (Yes)
  :Use existing Contact candidate;
else (No)
  :Create provisional Contact candidate;
endif

:Call external MDM using Named Credential;

if (MDM matched citizen?) then (Yes)
  :Update Contact with MDM citizen ID and verified attributes;
  :Set Case verification status to Verified;
  :Link Case to verified Contact;
else (No)
  :Set Case verification status to Manual Review;
  :Keep supplied phone/email on Case;
endif

if (MDM call failed transiently?) then (Yes)
  :Log Integration_Error__c;
  :Schedule retry or supervisor review;
endif

stop
@enduml
